{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"EventTarget.dispatchEvent","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/dispatchEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>addEventListener()</code></a></li><li><em><code>dispatchEvent()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/removeEventListener\"><code>removeEventListener()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>向一个指定的事件目标派发一个<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\">事件</a>,&nbsp; 并以合适的顺序<strong>同步调用</strong>目标元素相关的事件处理函数。标准事件处理规则 (包括事件捕获和可选的冒泡过程) 同样适用于通过手动的使用<code style=\"font-style: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">dispatchEvent()</code>方法派发的事件。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>cancelled</em> = !<em>target</em>.dispatchEvent(<em>event</em>)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>event</code>&nbsp;是要被派发的事件对象。</li>\n <li><code>target</code> 被用来初始化 事件 和 决定将会触发&nbsp;目标。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>当该事件是可取消的 (cancelable 为 true) 并且至少一个该事件的 事件处理方法&nbsp;调用了<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event/preventDefault\"><code>Event.preventDefault()</code></a>，则返回值为<code>false</code>；否则返回<code>true</code>。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>如果该被派发的事件的事件类型 (event's type) 在方法调用之前没有被经过初始化被指定，就会抛出一个&nbsp;<code>UNSPECIFIED_EVENT_TYPE_ERR</code>&nbsp;异常，或者如果事件类型是<code>null</code>或一个空字符串. event handler 就会抛出未捕获的异常； 这些 event handlers 运行在一个嵌套的调用栈中： 他们会阻塞调用直到他们处理完毕，但是异常不会冒泡。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"注意","isH3":false,"content":"<p>与浏览器原生事件不同，原生事件是由 DOM 派发的，并通过<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/EventLoop\">event loop</a>异步调用事件处理程序，而<code>dispatchEvent()</code>则是同步调用事件处理程序。在调用<code>dispatchEvent()</code>后，所有监听该事件的事件处理程序将在代码继续前执行并返回。</p>\n\n<p><code>dispatchEvent()</code>是 create-init-dispatch 过程的最后一步，用于将事件调度到实现的事件模型中。可以使用<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event/Event\">Event</a>构造函数来创建事件。</p>\n\n<p>另请参阅 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event\">Event object reference</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<p>参考&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Events/Creating_and_triggering_events\">Creating and triggering events</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Events/events.html#Events-EventTarget-dispatchEvent\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 Events: dispatchEvent</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<table>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-eventtarget-dispatchevent\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">EventTarget.dispatchEvent()</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition in the DOM 2 Events specification.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.EventTarget.dispatchEvent","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/dispatchEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"syntax"},{"text":"注意","id":"notes"},{"text":"例子","id":"example"},{"text":"规范","id":"specification"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"向一个指定的事件目标派发一个事件,  并以合适的顺序同步调用目标元素相关的事件处理函数。标准事件处理规则 (包括事件捕获和可选的冒泡过程) 同样适用于通过手动的使用dispatchEvent()方法派发的事件。","popularity":0.0013,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"EventTarget.dispatchEvent()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"element.dispatchEvent","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.dispatchEvent","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"EventTarget.dispatchEvent()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"EventTarget.dispatchEvent()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"element.dispatchEvent","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"EventTarget.dispatchEvent()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"EventTarget.dispatchEvent()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"EventTarget.dispatchEvent()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/eventtarget/dispatchevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/eventtarget/dispatchevent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget","title":"EventTarget"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/dispatchEvent","title":"EventTarget.dispatchEvent"}],"pageTitle":"EventTarget.dispatchEvent - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}